= Aesia AS3 Lib
╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                   				  READ ME		  		                        ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

The Aesia library is a general purpose actionscript library. This library contains four
distinct parts : 
 - The aesia.com.mon and aesia.com.patibility packages contains all the general utilities, 
   interfaces and classes used by the rest of the library. In aesia.com.patibility you can
   find all the codecs and the gettext implementation used by the rest of the library.
 - The aesia.com.mands and the aesia.com.munication packages contains all the command
   pattern's implementations and some concret implementations of commands dealing with
   server call and web services.
 - The aesia.com.motion and the aesia.com.media packages contains the classes in
   charge of making things move.
 - The aesia.com.ponents package contains the complete sets of components I created, with
   their own interfaces, classes and utilities. 


